{"tid":2151148,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要同情中國nmslese-古德明","createTime":"2020-08-11T08:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T17:38:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5315efa7334e80c0c5c9e5b2f48c09cf495a2ba4","tid":2151148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/H6X4ZAQOKBEO5EOQ2LBFKB5TBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FH6X4ZAQOKBEO5EOQ2LBFKB5TBU%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=ab2e3341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FH6X4ZAQOKBEO5EOQ2LBFKB5TBU%2F&h=485dc344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/H6X4ZAQOKBEO5EOQ2LBFKB5TBU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不要同情中國nmslese-古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d9Iob7eikoaYeaH_mhjBuzeXL10=/817x459/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FPPMAOYODJEHFEQB3XUBP3BLUQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd9Iob7eikoaYeaH_mhjBuzeXL10%3D%2F817x459%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFPPMAOYODJEHFEQB3XUBP3BLUQ.jpeg&h=5febe825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月二十日，長江白浪如山，直壓安徽王家壩，當局不待小民疏散，開閘泄洪，頓時水浸窪地。臺灣東森新聞臺播出一段錄影：影片中，有漢子流着淚，從水淹的家中，找回一些衣物，珍重置於浮板上，涉水而去；有七十一歲老翁，踩着三輛車，車上躺着九十三歲的老母，倉皇逃命，附近不見一位愛民若赤的公安；還有一黃衣女郎，似是記者，站在壩上，對着鏡頭，一指淼淼江水說：「聽見洪水洶湧的聲音了嗎？這不是泄洪，是蓄洪於數十萬安徽百姓家中。安徽人窮是窮，卻不儍。」字字句句都隱藏着悲愴的控訴。<br />\n<br />\n但請不要鼻酸。有臺灣人在影片之下留言說：「不要同情中國nmslese（愛黨的中國賤民）。他們選擇共產黨，就要接受所有的災難。」這樣的識見，在香港也時有所聞。我真不知道新中國人原來可以投票選擇統治者，只知道美國國務卿蓬佩奧還會說：「中國人勤奮，愛自由，與中共是兩回事。」將來，一定也會有黃種人笑言：「不要同情香港nmslese，他們選擇鄭月娥做行政長官，就要接受所有的後果。」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。可惜我見不及此，想到那推着浮板涉水而去的漢子，以及那三輛車老人和他母親，忍不住清淚盈眶。"},{"pid":"ee4fe208ca27bebdebc790f705d6eac7561163fa","tid":2151148,"uid":15605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"點解香港台灣都憎呢班所謂平民，自己心照啦"},{"pid":"ee9bc6459a5d68cf545f3b789b0945b93c5ffa5b","tid":2151148,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0624a08df467c21e2cd7fc78ab0b4b4d64aa0b92","tid":2151148,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f74bc0b9d93ac79db0ae2c5556925c7f71663943","tid":2151148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ddaf2d87669af8ee20fae215e3ac58601c2037","tid":2151148,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"他朝佢哋脫離苦難咪只會強加苦難落香港台灣維吾爾族同吐蕃人身上"}]}